    <td width="629"> <div align="left"> 
        <div align="left"> 
          <p><br>
            <font color="#333366" size="2" 
                  face="Geneva, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif">The University 
            of Illinois at Urbana-Champaign (UIUC) has a long and distiguished 
            history in computer architecture <font color="#333366">and compilers</font>.</font><font color="#333366" size="2" face="Geneva, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"> 
            UIUC is the home of the ILLIAC, the first computer built and owned 
            entirely by an educational institution in 1952, and Cedar, a hierarchical 
            shared-memory supercomputer completed in 1988. The <a href="http://www.cs.uiuc.edu/about/history.html">Illinois 
            Computing Timeline</a> provides a more complete history.</font></p>
        </div>
        <p><font color="#333366" size="2" face="Geneva, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif">Current 
          research projects span a broad spectrum of areas including low-power 
          design, adaptive systems, real-time and network processing, performance 
          evaluation methods, parallel computing, software reliability, performance 
          modeling and analysis, processor-memory integration, thread-level speculation, 
          dynamic optimization, compiler construction, simulation methodologies, 
          and software engineering. </font></p>
        <p><font color="#333366" size="2" face="Geneva, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><strong>Groups 
          and Projects:</strong></font></p>
        <ul>
          <li><font color="#333366" size="2" face="Geneva, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><a 
                        href="http://www.crhc.uiuc.edu/ACS">Advanced Computing 
            Systems group</a></font> 
            <ul>
              <li>rePLay: A Hardware Framework for Dynamic Optimization </li>
              <li>Advanced Simulation Techniques </li>
              <li>Architectural Support for High-Availability Systems </li>
            </ul>
          </li>
          <li><font color="#333366" size="2" face="Geneva, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><a href="http://www-sal.cs.uiuc.edu/%7Evadve/projects.html">Vikram 
